ZH: 你的要求有点过头了。
EN: Your demands are a bit excessive.

ZH: 这个项目的预算已经超过了预期。
EN: The budget for this project has gone overboard.

ZH: 不要把恶作剧玩得过头。
EN: Don't take pranks too far.

ZH: 他过头地夸奖了我的表现。
EN: He praised my performance excessively.

ZH: 我们不能过头地对待这个问题。
EN: We should not exaggerate about this issue.

ZH: 她在举办派对时总是搞得太过火。
EN: She always goes overboard when throwing parties.

ZH: 我觉得他过头地依赖了我。
EN: I feel like he relies on me excessively.

ZH: 别给她买太多礼物，不要过头。
EN: Don't buy too many gifts for her, don't go overboard.

ZH: 孩子们玩得太过头了，完全不顾安全问题。
EN: The children played too rough, completely ignoring safety concerns.

